data.description: Welcome to this Stunning home on one of the largest lots in the sought-after Fields Pond Sub. Nestled on a picturesque 1.05-acre lot in Cumming, this 4 bed/3.5 bath gem is a haven of sophistication. Boasting 3,617 square feet of meticulously crafted living space, it's a testament to luxury and comfort.    As you enter, you'll be greeted by a harmonious blend of modern design and traditional charm. The spacious rooms are flooded with natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere. The outdoor space is equally impressive, featuring lush greenery and a sense of serenity. Whether you're hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet moments, the expansive yard is a true retreat.    This Home Features a Beautiful Master Suite, a Formal dining room, and a spacious kitchen with an island and granite countertops, and a Media Room. Moreover, the property has received a series of thoughtful owner-led upgrades, enhancing both its aesthetic appeal and functional features. These improvements encompass a brand-new deck and a modernized master bathroom, introducing a touch of contemporary luxury to this already impressive home. Don't miss the chance to own a piece of timeless elegance in Cumming, GA.                              Don't miss the chance to own a piece of timeless elegance in Cumming, GA.
